addCatalogEntries

public void addCatalogEntries(IAeDeploymentId aDeploymentId,
                              IAeCatalogMapping[] aMappings,
                              boolean aReplaceFlag)
Adds an array of catalog mapping entries.

Parameters:
aDeploymentId - the id for the deployment or null if none to be recorded
aMappings - the mappings to add
aReplaceFlag - If this flag is set to true any previous wsdl entries mapped to the same location hint will be over written.
